quran[5{c,v,t}:
2,177,"neki yeh nahi hai ke tum ne apne chehray mashriq ki taraf kar liye ya maghrib ki taraf, balkay neki yeh hai ke aadmi Allah ko aur yom aakhir aur mulaika ko aur Allah ki nazil ki hui kitaab aur is ke payghambaroon ko dil se manay aur Allah ki mohabbat mein apna dil pasand maal rishte daaron aur yatimon par, miskeeno aur musafroon par, madad ke liye haath phelanay walon par aur ghulamoon ki rihayi par kharch kere, namaz qaim kere aurzakat day aur naik woh log hain ke jab ehad karen to ussay wafa karen, aur tangi o museebat ke waqt mein aur haq o baatil ki jung mein sabr karen yeh hainrasbaaz log aur yahi log mut-taqi hain"
2,178,"a y logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumahray liye qatal ke mqdmon mein qisaas ka hukum likh diya gaya hai azad aadmi ne qatal kya ho to is azad hi se badla liya jaye, ghulam qaatil ho to woh ghulam hi qatal kya jaye, aur aurat iss jurm ki murtakib ho tawa seen aurat hi se qisaas liya jaye haan agar kisi qaatil ke sath is ka bhai kuch narmi karne ke liye tayyar ho, to Maroof tareeqay ke mutabiq khoo baha ka tasfia hona chahiye aur qaatil ko lazim hai ke raasti ke sath khoo baha ada kere yeh tumahray Rab ki taraf se takhfeef aur rehmat hai is par bhi jo zayad-ti kere, is ke liye dard naak saza hai"
2,179,aqal o khiirad rakhnay walo! tumahray liye qisaas mein zindagi hai umeed hai ke tum is qanoon ki khilaaf warzi se parhaiz karo ge
2,180,"tum par farz kya gaya hai ke jab tum mein se kisi ki mout ka waqt aeye aur woh apne peechay maal chore raha ho, to walidain aur rishta daaron ke liye Maroof tareeqay se wasiyat kere yeh haq hai mut-taqi logon par"
2,181,"phir jinhon ne wasiyat suni aur baad mein ussay badal dala, tawa seen ka gunah un badalny walon par hoga Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
